Description: Located off Paris_ promenade, pop in to Napoleon_s, a lively piano bar and lounge boasting vintage Vegas showroom ambiance. Embellished with wood-paneled walls lined in gold, red curtains and a black and white checkered floor, Napoleon_s Lounge invites Las Vegas hotel guests to stop by for a cocktail, cigar or a dance.The drink menu features everything from an impressive wine list to plenty of Chambord-based cocktails, cognac, scotch, whiskey and bourbons. For the sweeter side, indulge in plenty of alcoholic dessert drinks. Try the Midnight in Paris with Godiva chocolate liqueur or the Banana Split Martini.Revelry is taken up a notch here as dueling pianists go head-to-head every night. The comedic piano players spin the hits from traditional party classics to current pop culture as they play almost all of the audience_s requests.Entertainment starts at 5 p.m. and ends at 1 a.m.
Location: 3655 Las Vegas Boulevard South Las Vegas , NV 89109
